00:09:47.970 --> 00:09:53.050 position:56%
This is not a place that is
thriving on the notion of fake news.

00:09:53.050 --> 00:09:55.230
This is not a fake news place.

00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:57.100
This is a place that is --

00:09:57.100 --> 00:10:02.230
